NOTE ON BUNDLED WAVEFORM DATA

The waveform data under `waveform_data/herbert/` and `waveform_data/p003914/`
is derived from the MIMIC-III Waveform Database (Moody et al., 2020),
distributed under the Open Data Commons Open Database License (ODbL) v1.0.
That data carries the ODbL's attribution and share-alike obligations
independently of the MIT license that governs this project's code.

See `waveform_data/LICENSE-ODbL.txt` for details and required attribution.
